      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong> to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Sprinkle<strong> half </strong>of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) into the mushrooms – these are your <strong>cheesy portobellos</strong></p><p>Set the tray aside until later</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1606305205644-x200.jpg",
