    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> thoroughly to remove any grit from between the leaves, then top, tail and slice into rounds</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> leek rounds</strong> to the casserole dish</p>",
